name: GAN you believe it?
description:
"Incredible oil painting of a forge, rembrandt lighting trending on artstation" (VQGAN+CLIP)
Skill: None
Time: 30 seconds active involvement, a few minutes waiting for result
Secrets: I know how this works and coded some stuff myself, but you don't need that to type in a prompt and hit run. 
Comments: AI art is really cool! But it can also give nice-looking results with very little effort, making it hard to distinguish between genuine art (with time, intent and skill invested) and just someone clicking a button.
